The wireless projector market is highly competitive, with players focusing on product differentiation, pricing strategies, and partnerships for market expansion.

16. What are the major distribution channels for wireless projectors?
The major distribution channels for wireless projectors include online retail, offline retail, and direct sales to businesses and institutions.

